	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A quick update (as reply for the people who already read this thread). It looks like the game will work fine if CNROM bus conflicts are emulated. The only difference then between $5FB being $00 or $FF is the background sound being a Galaxian-esqe-humm or a song.
<br />
<br />Problem solved <img src="./images/smilies/icon_biggrin.gif" alt=":D" title="Very Happy" /> ... I think.
<br />To people that own the game, do you hear a humm or music?

		

